    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName><name ref="Allo/Cillo">Allo, que Cillo</name></persName> vocatur,
                        filio <persName>quondam <name ref="Walpertus">Vualperti</name></persName>
                        riceve da <persName ref="#people/214" key="#Bishops">Gherardus</persName>
                        gratia Dei huius sancte Lucane ecclesie humilis <rs key="#Bishops"
                            >episcopus</rs>, per cartula livellario nomine, casa et res illa in loco
                        et finibus <placeName ref="#places/239">Quaratiana, ubi dicitur ad Monte
                            Alto</placeName>, quas <persName><name ref="Bellulo"
                            >Bellulo</name></persName> ad manus suas abuit, pertenentes suprascripti
                            <rs key="#Mother_churches">episcopatui</rs> vestro <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/68" key="#Domus #Mother_churches">Sancti
                            Martini</orgName>; casa vero ipsa cum fundamento et edeficio suo seu
                        curte, orto, terris, vineis, olivis, silvis, virgareis, pratis, cultas res
                        vel incultas omnia quantum (…) in integrum mihi eas dedisti (…). Obbligo:
                        ego vel meis heredes in ipsa casa residere et abitare debeamus et tam ipsa
                        casa quam et predicta res (…) bene laborare et gubernare seo meliorare
                        debeamus et nobis eas privatum nomine usufructandi (…). Censo: pro omni
                        censum et iustitia exinde tibi vel ad subcessoribus tuis ad pars ipsius
                        episcopatui vestro per singulos annos, in mense november, censum vobis
                        reddere debeamus, hic <rs key="#Cities">civitate</rs> Luca, ad suprascripto
                            <rs key="#Domus">domo</rs> per nos aut per misso nostro, vobis vel ad
                        misso vestro aut ad ministerialem (…) argentum denarios bonos expendiviles
                        numero viginti quatuor; et per omnem mense magio vobis reddere debeamus
                        montone uno bono; et a mandato vestro venire debeamus hic Luca legem et
                        iustitiam faciendum tantum (…). Pena: ego qui supra Allo una cum meis
                        heredes conponere tibi (…) penam argentum soledos viginti (…). <persName
                            key="#Writer #Witness #Notary"><name ref="Teuderandus"
                                >Teuderandus</name></persName> notarius scrive due <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">cartulas</rs>. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4" key="#Cities #Domus #Mother_churches #Bishops"
                            >Luca</placeName>. </ab>
                    <ab>Sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>: <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Allo">Aloni</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Willeradus">Vuillerado</name></persName>,
                        filio <persName>quondam <name ref="Osprandus">Osprandi</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness" ref="#people/149">Cunimundo</persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Stephanus"
                        >Stefanu</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Grimulfus"
                                >Grimolfo</name></persName>.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
